OL,3,CDetective series Bergerac confirmed
OL,4,Cfor return featuring Jersey locations
OL,6,FDetective series Bergerac will be
OL,7,Freturning to its original setting of
OL,8,FJersey but "with a contemporary
OL,9,Ftwist", UKTV has announced.
OL,11,FA new series has been commissioned
OL,12,Fwith six episodes being filmed over
OL,13,Fthe summer.
OL,15,FThe original show starring John
OL,16,FNettles ran for nine series on the BBC
OL,17,Fbetween 1981 and 1991.
OL,19,FThe series followed Jim Bergerac, a
OL,20,Ffictional detective working in Jersey.
