OL,6,FTalks are still ongoing with the
OL,7,Fisland's government regarding whether
OL,8,Fthere will be any public funding.
OL,10,FThe Minister for Sustainable Economic
OL,11,FDevelopment, Deputy Kirsten Morel,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Government officers have been
OL,13,Fworking closely with Visit Jersey and
OL,14,Findustry experts to assess the
OL,15,FBergerac project and its potential for
OL,16,Fan investment of significant amounts
OL,17,Fof public money.
