OL,6,F"This work is ongoing but we are
OL,7,Fpleased to see that the producers and
OL,8,FTV channel have announced today that
OL,9,Fthey are committed to producing the
OL,10,FBergerac remake."
OL,12,FITV News understands that there is
OL,13,Flikely to be some financial support
OL,14,Ffrom the government but the political
OL,15,Fwill is for it to be 'at the right
OL,16,Flevel'.
OL,18,FThe series will be available for
OL,19,Fstreaming on UKTV Play and air on
OL,20,FDrama next year.
